title: Dinosaur - Triceratops

longDescription:

This is a High Poly 3D Model of a Triceratops with meshes optimized to a Low Poly version:

•Triceratops - HP 6402 tris;

•Triceratops - LP 2250 tris.


Model has 44 Bones. 


Textures:

•Triceratops - 4 Color Textures, 2 Normals, 1 Ambient Oclussion (all 4k by 4k).
